Title: How I Made $80,000 On Side Projects In 2020 — Compiled;
Description: Money is a taboo topic in many cultures, however I think it’s important to discuss how I was able to publish side projects that allowed me to pay off my overwhelming medical debt, buy a house, and build my savings.

Title: ASP.NET Core Blazor routing

Title: New evidence supports idea that America's first civilization was made up of 'sophisticated' engineers
Description: The Native Americans who occupied the area known as Poverty Point in northern Louisiana more than 3,000 years ago long have been believed to be simple hunters and gatherers. But new Washington University in St. Louis archaeological findings paint a drastically different picture of America's first civilization.
